  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for iproute2",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for iproute2 fixes the following issue\n\n- CVE-2024-58251: denial of service via terminal escape sequences (bsc#1254324).\n\nChanges for iproute2:\n\n- support display of bound but unconnected sockets (bsc#1204562).\n- avoid spurious cgroup warning (bsc#1234383).\n- add post-6.4 follow-up fixes (bsc#1243005).\n- devlink: support ipsec_crypto and ipsec_packet cap (bsc#1248660).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
